    user_response: "Apply the \"Immersive UI\" design theme to the app.\n[AIS_METADATA_SECTION_START]\nDesign name: Immersive UI\nDesign instructions: Extract ONLY the styling (colors, fonts, spacing, borders, shadows, backgrounds, gradients) and layout patterns (flexbox/grid structure, component arrangement) from the Design HTML below. Do NOT replace or restructure the existing app\'s HTML elements \342\200\224 preserve all existing components, content, and functionality. Only modify CSS/styling and adjust layout containers as needed to match the theme\'s aesthetic.\nDesign HTML:                   <!doctype html>\\n                  <html style=\\\"height: 100%; margin: 0;\\\">\\n                    <head>\\n                      <meta charset=\\\"UTF-8\\\" />\\n                      <meta name=\\\"viewport\\\" content=\\\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\\\" />\\n                      <script src=\\\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@tailwindcss/browser@4\\\"></script>\\n                      <link href=\\\"https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Material+Symbols+Outlined:opsz,wght,FILL,GRAD@20..48,100..700,0..1,-50..200\\\" rel=\\\"stylesheet\\\" />\\n                      <style>\\n                        body { margin: 0; height: 100%; display: flex; flex-direction: column; overflow: hidden; }\\n                        /* Fallback classes in case Tailwind fails to load in sandbox */\\n                        .h-full { height: 100%; }\\n                        .w-full { width: 100%; }\\n                        .flex { display: flex; }\\n                        .flex-col { flex-direction: column; }\\n                        .flex-1 { flex: 1 1 0%; }\\n                      </style>\\n                    </head>\\n                    <body>\\n                      <div class=\\\"w-[1024px] h-[768px] bg-[#05070A] text-slate-200 font-sans flex flex-col overflow-hidden relative\\\">\\n  <div class=\\\"absolute inset-0 z-0 bg-[#0A0C10]\\\">\\n    <div class=\\\"absolute inset-0 opacity-20\\\" style=\\\"background-image: radial-gradient(#1E293B 1px, transparent 1px); background-size: 32px 32px;\\\"></div>\\n    <div class=\\\"absolute inset-0 flex items-center justify-center pointer-events-none\\\">\\n      <div class=\\\"relative w-[1200px] h-[800px] flex items-center justify-center transform perspective-[1000px] rotate-x-[45deg] rotate-z-[-15deg]\\\">\\n        <div class=\\\"grid grid-cols-6 grid-rows-6 gap-4 w-full h-full\\\">\\n          <div class=\\\"bg-slate-800/80 rounded-sm relative shadow-[40px_80px_0px_rgba(0,0,0,0.4)] h-32 mt-auto\\\"></div>\\n          <div class=\\\"bg-slate-700/80 rounded-sm relative shadow-[50px_100px_0px_rgba(0,0,0,0.4)] h-48 mt-auto\\\"></div>\\n          <div class=\\\"bg-slate-800/80 rounded-sm relative shadow-[30px_60px_0px_rgba(0,0,0,0.4)] h-24 mt-auto\\\"></div>\\n          <div class=\\\"bg-amber-400/20 border border-amber-500/50 rounded-sm h-0 mt-auto flex items-center justify-center text-[10px] text-amber-500 font-mono\\\">SUN ZONE</div>\\n          <div class=\\\"bg-slate-800/80 rounded-sm relative shadow-[45px_90px_0px_rgba(0,0,0,0.4)] h-40 mt-auto\\\"></div>\\n          <div class=\\\"bg-slate-700/80 rounded-sm relative shadow-[55px_110px_0px_rgba(0,0,0,0.4)] h-56 mt-auto\\\"></div>\\n          <div class=\\\"bg-slate-700/80 rounded-sm relative shadow-[35px_70px_0px_rgba(0,0,0,0.4)] h-28 mt-auto\\\"></div>\\n          <div class=\\\"bg-slate-800/80 rounded-sm relative shadow-[60px_120px_0px_rgba(0,0,0,0.4)] h-64 mt-auto\\\"></div>\\n          <div class=\\\"bg-amber-400/20 border border-amber-500/50 rounded-sm h-0 mt-auto\\\"></div>\\n          <div class=\\\"bg-slate-800/80 rounded-sm relative shadow-[40px_80px_0px_rgba(0,0,0,0.4)] h-32 mt-auto\\\"></div>\\n          <div class=\\\"bg-slate-700/80 rounded-sm relative shadow-[30px_60px_0px_rgba(0,0,0,0.4)] h-24 mt-auto\\\"></div>\\n          <div class=\\\"bg-slate-800/80 rounded-sm relative shadow-[50px_100px_0px_rgba(0,0,0,0.4)] h-48 mt-auto\\\"></div>\\n        </div>\\n      </div>\\n    </div>\\n  </div>\\n  <nav class=\\\"z-10 h-16 border-b border-white/10 bg-black/40 backdrop-blur-xl flex items-center justify-between px-8\\\">\\n    <div class=\\\"flex items-center gap-6\\\">\\n      <div class=\\\"flex items-center gap-2\\\">\\n        <div class=\\\"w-8 h-8 bg-amber-500 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center\\\">\\n          <div class=\\\"w-4 h-4 rounded-full border-2 border-black\\\"></div>\\n        </div>\\n        <span class=\\\"font-bold tracking-tight text-lg\\\">HELIOS<span class=\\\"text-amber-500\\\">PRO</span></span>\\n      </div>\\n      <div class=\\\"h-8 w-px bg-white/10 mx-2\\\"></div>\\n      <div class=\\\"relative\\\">\\n        <input type=\\\"text\\\" value=\\\"Lower Manhattan, NY\\\" class=\\\"bg-white/5 border border-white/10 rounded-full py-2 px-10 text-sm w-64 focus:outline-none focus:border-amber-500/50\\\" />\\n        <svg class=\\\"absolute left-3 top-2.5 w-4 h-4 text-slate-500\\\" fill=\\\"none\\\" stroke=\\\"currentColor\\\" viewBox=\\\"0 0 24 24\\\"><path stroke-linecap=\\\"round\\\" stroke-linejoin=\\\"round\\\" stroke-width=\\\"2\\\" d=\\\"M21 21l-6-6m2-5a7 7 0 11-14 0 7 7 0 0114 0z\\\"/></svg>\\n      </div>\\n    </div>\\n    <div class=\\\"flex items-center gap-4\\\">\\n      <button class=\\\"flex items-center gap-2 bg-white/5 border border-white/10 rounded-full px-4 py-1.5 text-xs font-medium hover:bg-white/10\\\">\\n        <span class=\\\"w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-green-500\\\"></span>\\n        GEOMETRY ENGINE: GPU (60 FPS)\\n      </button>\\n      <button class=\\\"bg-amber-500 text-black text-xs font-bold px-4 py-2 rounded-full\\\">SYNC TO NOW</button>\\n    </div>\\n  </nav>\\n  <main class=\\\"flex-1 relative flex\\\">\\n    <div class=\\\"z-10 absolute right-8 top-8 w-80 flex flex-col gap-4\\\">\\n      <div class=\\\"bg-black/60 backdrop-blur-2xl border border-white/10 rounded-2xl p-6 shadow-2xl\\\">\\n        <div class=\\\"flex justify-between items-start mb-6\\\">\\n          <div>\\n            <h2 class=\\\"text-xs font-bold text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-widest\\\">Solar Metrics</h2>\\n            <p class=\\\"text-2xl font-mono text-amber-400 font-bold tracking-tighter\\\">16:42:04</p>\\n          </div>\\n          <div class=\\\"text-right\\\">\\n            <p class=\\\"text-[10px] text-slate-500 font-mono\\\">OCT 12, 2023</p>\\n            <p class=\\\"text-[10px] text-slate-500 font-mono\\\">40.71\302\260 N, 74.00\302\260 W</p>\\n          </div>\\n        </div>\\n        <div class=\\\"space-y-4\\\">\\n          <div class=\\\"flex justify-between items-center py-2 border-b border-white/5\\\">\\n            <span class=\\\"text-xs text-slate-400\\\">Azimuth</span>\\n            <span class=\\\"text-sm font-mono\\\">242.38\302\260 SW</span>\\n          </div>\\n          <div class=\\\"flex justify-between items-center py-2 border-b border-white/5\\\">\\n            <span class=\\\"text-xs text-slate-400\\\">Elevation</span>\\n            <span class=\\\"text-sm font-mono\\\">12.42\302\260</span>\\n          </div>\\n          <div class=\\\"grid grid-cols-2 gap-4 pt-2\\\">\\n            <div class=\\\"p-3 bg-white/5 rounded-xl border border-white/5\\\">\\n              <p class=\\\"text-[10px] text-blue-400 uppercase font-bold mb-1\\\">Blue Hour</p>\\n              <p class=\\\"text-sm font-mono\\\">06:42 | 18:24</p>\\n            </div>\\n            <div class=\\\"p-3 bg-amber-500/10 rounded-xl border border-amber-500/20\\\">\\n              <p class=\\\"text-[10px] text-amber-500 uppercase font-bold mb-1\\\">Golden Hour</p>\\n              <p class=\\\"text-sm font-mono\\\">17:15 - 18:02</p>\\n            </div>\\n          </div>\\n          <button class=\\\"w-full mt-2 py-3 bg-white text-black text-xs font-bold rounded-xl tracking-widest uppercase hover:bg-slate-200\\\">Snap to Golden Hour</button>\\n        </div>\\n      </div>\\n      <div class=\\\"bg-black/60 backdrop-blur-2xl border border-white/10 rounded-2xl p-4\\\">\\n        <div class=\\\"flex items-center justify-between mb-4\\\">\\n          <h3 class=\\\"text-[10px] font-bold text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-widest\\\">Layer Controls</h3>\\n          <div class=\\\"w-8 h-4 bg-amber-500 rounded-full relative\\\"><div class=\\\"absolute right-1 top-1 w-2 h-2 bg-black rounded-full\\\"></div></div>\\n        </div>\\n        <div class=\\\"space-y-2\\\">\\n          <div class=\\\"flex items-center gap-3\\\">\\n            <div class=\\\"w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-slate-800 flex items-center justify-center\\\">\\n              <div class=\\\"w-4 h-4 border border-slate-500\\\"></div>\\n            </div>\\n            <div>\\n              <p class=\\\"text-xs font-medium\\\">3D Buildings (OSM)</p>\\n              <p class=\\\"text-[10px] text-slate-500\\\">Extruded geometry layer</p>\\n            </div>\\n          </div>\\n          <div class=\\\"flex items-center gap-3\\\">\\n            <div class=\\\"w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-amber-500/20 flex items-center justify-center\\\">\\n              <div class=\\\"w-4 h-4 bg-amber-500/40 rounded-sm\\\"></div>\\n            </div>\\n            <div>\\n              <p class=\\\"text-xs font-medium\\\">Solar Heatmap</p>\\n              <p class=\\\"text-[10px] text-slate-500\\\">Unshaded ground area</p>\\n            </div>\\n          </div>\\n        </div>\\n      </div>\\n    </div>\\n    <div class=\\\"z-10 absolute bottom-12 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 w-[900px] h-28 bg-black/60 backdrop-blur-2xl border border-white/10 rounded-3xl p-6 flex flex-col justify-between shadow-2xl\\\">\\n      <div class=\\\"flex justify-between items-center mb-2 px-2\\\">\\n        <span class=\\\"text-[10px] font-mono text-slate-500\\\">00:00</span>\\n        <span class=\\\"text-[10px] font-mono text-slate-500\\\">04:00</span>\\n        <div class=\\\"flex flex-col items-center\\\">\\n          <span class=\\\"text-[10px] font-mono text-blue-400\\\">SUNRISE</span>\\n          <div class=\\\"w-px h-2 bg-blue-400\\\"></div>\\n        </div>\\n        <span class=\\\"text-[10px] font-mono text-slate-500\\\">08:00</span>\\n        <span class=\\\"text-[10px] font-mono text-slate-500\\\">12:00</span>\\n        <span class=\\\"text-[10px] font-mono text-amber-500\\\">NOW</span>\\n        <div class=\\\"flex flex-col items-center\\\">\\n          <span class=\\\"text-[10px] font-mono text-amber-500\\\">SUNSET</span>\\n          <div class=\\\"w-px h-2 bg-amber-500\\\"></div>\\n        </div>\\n        <span class=\\\"text-[10px] font-mono text-slate-500\\\">20:00</span>\\n        <span class=\\\"text-[10px] font-mono text-slate-500\\\">23:59</span>\\n      </div>\\n      <div class=\\\"relative h-10 flex items-center\\\">\\n        <div class=\\\"absolute inset-0 bg-white/5 rounded-full overflow-hidden flex\\\">\\n          <div class=\\\"h-full bg-blue-500/10 w-[25%]\\\"></div>\\n          <div class=\\\"h-full bg-gradient-to-r from-amber-500/20 via-amber-200/40 to-amber-500/20 w-[45%]\\\"></div>\\n          <div class=\\\"h-full bg-blue-500/10 w-[30%]\\\"></div>\\n        </div>\\n        <div class=\\\"absolute inset-0 flex items-center px-4 pointer-events-none\\\">\\n          <div class=\\\"h-2 w-full border-t border-dashed border-white/20\\\"></div>\\n        </div>\\n        <div class=\\\"absolute left-[65%] w-10 h-10 -mt-5 flex items-center justify-center bg-white rounded-full shadow-[0_0_20px_rgba(255,255,255,0.4)] cursor-pointer group\\\">\\n          <div class=\\\"w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-amber-500 flex items-center justify-center\\\">\\n             <div class=\\\"w-2 h-2 bg-white rounded-full\\\"></div>\\n          </div>\\n          <div class=\\\"absolute -top-10 bg-white text-black px-3 py-1 rounded text-sm font-bold shadow-lg\\\">16:42</div>\\n        </div>\\n      </div>\\n    </div>\\n  </main>\\n  <div class=\\\"absolute bottom-4 left-8 z-10 flex gap-4 text-[10px] text-slate-500 font-mono\\\">\\n    <span>LAT: 40.7128\302\260</span>\\n    <span>LNG: -74.0060\302\260</span>\\n    <span>ELEV: 10m</span>\\n    <span>PRECISION: HIGH (RT)</span>\\n  </div>\\n</div>\\n                    </body>\\n                  </html>\n[AIS_METADATA_SECTION_END]"
